title: How to Survive Restructuring
description: How to Survive Restructuring Manhwa The moment I was notified of being included in the company’s restructuring list, a deafening roar, as if the sky was falling, marked the transformation of the world. [The sale of this Earth has been decided.] [Accordingly, a restructuring of personnel is underway.] Life-threatening restructuring. Missions that grant extraordinary powers upon completion. If this is some kind of miraculous joke, I will give it my all! “I’ve found it. A way for all of us to survive together.” The rapid rise of Lee Eun-ho, a restructuring target, begins now! 구조 조정에서 살아남는 법
